w<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=yes, viewport-fit=cover">
<title>Your Special Day ✦ Yokhebed</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400;0,600;0,700;1,400;1,600&family=Cormorant+Garamond:ital,wght@0,300;0,400;1,300;1,400&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}
:root{
  --bg:#2a0508;
  --cream:#f5e6d3;
  --gold:#e8c8a8;
  --pink:#e8a8b8;
  --cake-brown:#8B5A2B;
  --cake-cream:#FFF8E7;
}
html,body{width:100%;height:100%;overflow:hidden;background:var(--bg);font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;color:var(--cream);-webkit-tap-highlight-color:transparent}

body::before{content:'';position:fixed;inset:0;background:radial-gradient(ellipse at 72% 22%,rgba(140,30,50,.45) 0%,rgba(0,0,0,0) 45%),radial-gradient(ellipse at 30% 80%,rgba(170,40,55,.35) 0%,rgba(0,0,0,0) 50%),radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 45%,#5a1422 0%,#3a0c16 38%,#22070f 70%,#0e0306 100%);z-index:0;animation:bgPulse 14s ease-in-out infinite}
@keyframes bgPulse{0%,100%{filter:brightness(1) saturate(1)}50%{filter:brightness(1.06) saturate(1.1)}}

#stars,#sparkles-container{position:fixed;inset:0;pointer-events:none;z-index:1}
.star{position:absolute;background:#fff;border-radius:50%;animation:twinkle var(--dur,3s) ease-in-out infinite var(--del,0s)}
@keyframes twinkle{0%,100%{opacity:.15;transform:scale(1)}50%{opacity:.9;transform:scale(1.25)}}
.fsparkle{position:absolute;font-size:13px;opacity:0;animation:floatUp var(--fdur,9s) ease-in-out var(--fdel,0s) infinite;pointer-events:none}
@keyframes floatUp{0%{opacity:0;transform:translateY(0) rotate(0deg) scale(.8)}10%{opacity:.7}88%{opacity:.5}100%{opacity:0;transform:translateY(-100vh) rotate(380deg) scale(1.1)}}

.page{position:fixed;inset:0;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;justify-content:center;z-index:10;opacity:0;pointer-events:none;transition:opacity .9s cubic-bezier(0.2,0.9,0.3,1.1);padding:20px 16px;overflow-y:auto}
.page.active{opacity:1;pointer-events:all}
#overlay{position:fixed;inset:0;z-index:999;background:#000;opacity:0;pointer-events:none;transition:opacity .45s ease}

.sec-lbl{font-size:10px;letter-spacing:5px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--gold);margin-bottom:14px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;opacity:.85}
.sec-lbl::before,.sec-lbl::after{content:'✦';font-size:7px;opacity:.6}
.main-title{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:clamp(1.8rem,5vw,3.5rem);font-weight:600;font-style:italic;color:var(--cream);text-align:center;line-height:1.2;text-shadow:0 0 50px rgba(232,200,168,.3)}
.subtitle{font-size:13px;color:var(--gold);text-align:center;margin-top:8px;line-height:1.6;opacity:.8;max-width:420px}

.btn{margin-top:22px;padding:12px 32px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.07);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.14);border-radius:30px;color:var(--cream);font-size:11px;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;cursor:pointer;transition:all .35s ease;backdrop-filter:blur(12px);display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px}
.btn:hover,.btn:active{background:rgba(232,168,184,.22);border-color:var(--pink);transform:translateY(-3px)}
.btn-pink{background:rgba(232,168,184,.12);border-color:rgba(232,168,184,.28)}
.btn-disabled{opacity:0.4;pointer-events:none;filter:grayscale(0.3)}
.highlight-btn{animation:btnPulse 0.7s ease-in-out infinite;background:rgba(232,168,184,.25)!important;border-color:var(--pink)!important}
@keyframes btnPulse{0%,100%{box-shadow:0 0 0 0 rgba(232,168,184,0.7),0 0 20px rgba(232,168,184,0.3)}50%{box-shadow:0 0 0 14px rgba(232,168,184,0),0 0 30px rgba(232,168,184,0.5)}}

/* COUNTDOWN */
.cd-row{display:flex;gap:14px;margin-top:28px;flex-wrap:wrap;justify-content:center}
.cd-box{background:rgba(0,0,0,.32);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.1);border-radius:18px;padding:16px 20px;min-width:74px;text-align:center;backdrop-filter:blur(14px);transition:background 0.3s,border-color 0.3s}
.cd-num{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:2.2rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--cream);display:block;line-height:1}
.cd-num.pop{animation:numPop .2s ease}
@keyframes numPop{0%,100%{transform:scale(1)}50%{transform:scale(1.16)}}
.cd-lbl{font-size:8px;letter-spacing:2.5px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--gold);margin-top:6px;display:block;opacity:.7}
.cd-sep{font-size:1.6rem;color:var(--pink);align-self:center;opacity:.5;animation:pulse 2s ease-in-out infinite}
@keyframes pulse{0%,100%{opacity:.5}50%{opacity:.9}}
/* Final 0:00:00:00 state — boxes turn red (brief pulse, not continuous shake) */
.cd-zero .cd-box{background:rgba(220,40,50,.35)!important;border-color:rgba(255,80,90,.7)!important;box-shadow:0 0 18px rgba(220,40,50,.4);animation:cdZeroPulse 0.5s ease-out}
@keyframes cdZeroPulse{0%{transform:scale(1)}30%{transform:scale(1.08)}100%{transform:scale(1)}}
.cd-zero .cd-num{color:#ffdede}
/* Last 3 seconds: seconds box shows ms countdown, no shaking */
.millisecond-box{background:rgba(232,168,184,.35)!important;border:2px solid var(--pink)!important;border-radius:18px!important}

/* PAGE 2 - CAKE — compact, never covers header */
#page2{justify-content:center;gap:0;padding:16px}
.p2-header{text-align:center;margin-bottom:16px}
.p2-header .sec-lbl{justify-content:center;margin-bottom:4px}
.p2-header .main-title{font-size:clamp(1.3rem,4vw,2.2rem)}
.page2-content{display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;justify-content:center;width:100%}
.cake-container{position:relative;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;margin:0 0 12px;cursor:pointer;transition:transform 0.2s ease}
.cake-container:active{transform:scale(0.97)}
.cake-plate{width:130px;height:9px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#C0A080,#A08060);border-radius:50%;box-shadow:0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);margin-top:-3px}
.cake-layer{width:118px;height:24px;background:linear-gradient(180deg,var(--cake-brown),#6B3A1F);border-radius:9px 9px 5px 5px;position:relative;box-shadow:0 3px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.2)}
.cake-layer-top{width:104px;height:22px;background:linear-gradient(180deg,#D4A574,#B87C4A);border-radius:7px 7px 4px 4px;margin-top:-4px;position:relative}
.cake-icing{position:absolute;top:-5px;left:5px;right:5px;height:8px;background:linear-gradient(180deg,var(--cake-cream),#FFE4C4);border-radius:10px;display:flex;justify-content:center;gap:5px}
.icing-dot{width:4px;height:4px;background:#FFB6C1;border-radius:50%;margin-top:2px}
.candle{position:absolute;top:-20px;left:50%;transform:translateX(-50%);width:5px;height:20px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#FF6B6B,#FF4444);border-radius:3px 3px 2px 2px}
.flame{position:absolute;top:-8px;left:-2px;width:9px;height:11px;background:radial-gradient(circle, #FFD700, #FF8C00, #FF4500);border-radius:50% 50% 50% 50% / 60% 60% 40% 40%;animation:flicker 0.25s ease-in-out infinite alternate}
@keyframes flicker{0%{transform:scale(1);opacity:0.8}100%{transform:scale(1.1);opacity:1}}
.cake-photo{position:absolute;bottom:3px;left:50%;transform:translateX(-50%);width:28px;height:28px;border-radius:50%;border:2px solid var(--cream);overflow:hidden;background:#333}
.cake-photo img{width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover}
.gift-hint{font-size:11px;color:var(--gold);letter-spacing:1px;opacity:0.7}

/* Hanging string lights above cake */
.cake-lights{position:relative;width:180px;height:30px;margin-bottom:20px}
.lights-string{position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:2px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,transparent 0%,rgba(200,160,100,0.4) 20%,rgba(200,160,100,0.4) 80%,transparent 100%)}
.light-bulb{position:absolute;top:0px;width:7px;height:10px;border-radius:50% 50% 40% 40%;transform:translateX(-50%)}
.light-bulb::before{content:'';position:absolute;top:-4px;left:50%;transform:translateX(-50%);width:2px;height:4px;background:rgba(180,140,80,0.6)}
.light-bulb.lb1{left:15%;background:#FFD700;box-shadow:0 0 6px #FFD700,0 0 12px rgba(255,215,0,0.5);animation:bulbFlicker 1.8s ease-in-out infinite}
.light-bulb.lb2{left:30%;background:#FF69B4;box-shadow:0 0 6px #FF69B4,0 0 12px rgba(255,105,180,0.5);animation:bulbFlicker 2.2s ease-in-out infinite 0.4s}
.light-bulb.lb3{left:45%;background:#87CEEB;box-shadow:0 0 6px #87CEEB,0 0 12px rgba(135,206,235,0.5);animation:bulbFlicker 1.5s ease-in-out infinite 0.8s}
.light-bulb.lb4{left:60%;background:#90EE90;box-shadow:0 0 6px #90EE90,0 0 12px rgba(144,238,144,0.5);animation:bulbFlicker 2s ease-in-out infinite 1.2s}
.light-bulb.lb5{left:75%;background:#FFB347;box-shadow:0 0 6px #FFB347,0 0 12px rgba(255,179,71,0.5);animation:bulbFlicker 1.6s ease-in-out infinite 0.2s}
.light-bulb.lb6{left:88%;background:#DDA0DD;box-shadow:0 0 6px #DDA0DD,0 0 12px rgba(221,160,221,0.5);animation:bulbFlicker 2.4s ease-in-out infinite 0.6s}
@keyframes bulbFlicker{0%,100%{opacity:0.6;transform:translateX(-50%) scale(0.85)}50%{opacity:1;transform:translateX(-50%) scale(1)}}

/* Confetti streamers decoration on cake page */
.cake-decor{position:absolute;inset:0;pointer-events:none;overflow:hidden;z-index:0}
.streamer{position:absolute;width:3px;border-radius:2px;opacity:0.5;animation:streamerDrift var(--sd, 4s) ease-in-out infinite var(--sdel,0s)}
@keyframes streamerDrift{0%,100%{transform:rotate(var(--sr,10deg)) scaleY(1)}50%{transform:rotate(calc(var(--sr,10deg) + 8deg)) scaleY(0.85)}}

/* PAGE 3 - PUZZLE COLLAGE */
#page3{overflow:hidden;justify-content:flex-start;padding:0}
.p3-inner{display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;width:100%;height:100vh;overflow:hidden}
.p3-header{flex-shrink:0;padding:10px 16px 4px;text-align:center}
.p3-header .sec-lbl{margin-bottom:4px;justify-content:center}
.p3-header .main-title{font-size:clamp(1.1rem,3vw,1.8rem);margin-bottom:0}

.collage-scroll{flex:1;overflow-y:auto;overflow-x:hidden;width:100%;scroll-behavior:smooth;-webkit-overflow-scrolling:touch}
.collage-scroll::-webkit-scrollbar{width:3px}
.collage-scroll::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb{background:rgba(232,168,184,.3);border-radius:3px}

.collage-grid{display:grid;width:100%;max-width:820px;margin:0 auto;padding:10px 12px 16px;gap:10px;
  grid-template-columns:repeat(6,1fr);
}

.col-item{position:relative;overflow:hidden;border-radius:8px;background:#1a1a1a;opacity:0;transition:transform 0.4s cubic-bezier(.25,.46,.45,.94),box-shadow 0.4s ease}
.col-item.developed:hover{transform:scale(1.04) rotate(-0.5deg);z-index:5;box-shadow:0 12px 40px rgba(0,0,0,0.5)}
.col-item.reveal-pol{animation:fadeInPol 0.5s forwards}
@keyframes fadeInPol{from{opacity:0;transform:scale(0.9)}to{opacity:1;transform:scale(1)}}

/* Polaroid white frame effect */
.col-item .pol-frame{position:absolute;inset:0;border:5px solid #fff;border-bottom:20px solid #fff;border-radius:6px;pointer-events:none;z-index:3;opacity:0;transition:opacity 0.4s ease;box-shadow:inset 0 0 0 1px rgba(0,0,0,0.08),0 4px 14px rgba(0,0,0,0.45)}
.col-item.developed .pol-frame{opacity:1}
/* Glow behind polaroid */
.col-item::after{content:'';position:absolute;inset:-2px;border-radius:7px;pointer-events:none;opacity:0;transition:opacity 0.8s ease;z-index:0}
.col-item.developed::after{opacity:1}
.col-item:nth-child(3n+1).developed::after{animation:glowPink 2.5s ease-in-out infinite alternate}
.col-item:nth-child(3n+2).developed::after{animation:glowGold 3s ease-in-out infinite alternate}
.col-item:nth-child(3n+3).developed::after{animation:glowLilac 2s ease-in-out infinite alternate}
@keyframes glowPink{0%{box-shadow:0 0 6px rgba(232,168,184,0.3)}100%{box-shadow:0 0 20px rgba(232,168,184,0.8),0 0 40px rgba(232,168,184,0.3)}}
@keyframes glowGold{0%{box-shadow:0 0 6px rgba(232,200,168,0.3)}100%{box-shadow:0 0 20px rgba(232,200,168,0.8),0 0 40px rgba(232,200,168,0.3)}}
@keyframes glowLilac{0%{box-shadow:0 0 6px rgba(200,160,220,0.3)}100%{box-shadow:0 0 20px rgba(200,160,220,0.8),0 0 40px rgba(200,160,220,0.3)}}

.col-item img{width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;display:block;filter:blur(8px) sepia(.15) brightness(0.6);transition:filter 0.7s ease;position:relative;z-index:1}
.col-item.developed img{filter:none}

/* Highlight shimmer on photo reveal */
.col-item .shimmer{position:absolute;inset:0;background:linear-gradient(105deg,transparent 30%,rgba(255,255,255,0.35) 50%,transparent 70%);transform:translateX(-100%);z-index:2;pointer-events:none;border-radius:4px}
.col-item.developed .shimmer{animation:shimmerSlide 0.8s ease forwards 0.4s}
@keyframes shimmerSlide{from{transform:translateX(-100%)}to{transform:translateX(100%)}}

/* Corner fairy lights */
.col-item .light-tl,.col-item .light-tr,.col-item .light-bl,.col-item .light-br{position:absolute;width:7px;height:7px;border-radius:50%;pointer-events:none;opacity:0;transition:opacity 0.6s ease;z-index:4}
.col-item.developed .light-tl,.col-item.developed .light-tr,.col-item.developed .light-bl,.col-item.developed .light-br{opacity:1}
.col-item .light-tl{top:22px;left:5px;background:#FFD700;box-shadow:0 0 5px #FFD700;animation:fairyBlink 1.5s ease-in-out infinite}
.col-item .light-tr{top:22px;right:5px;background:#FFB6C1;box-shadow:0 0 5px #FFB6C1;animation:fairyBlink 1.8s ease-in-out infinite 0.3s}
.col-item .light-bl{bottom:22px;left:5px;background:#E0BBFF;box-shadow:0 0 5px #E0BBFF;animation:fairyBlink 2.1s ease-in-out infinite 0.6s}
.col-item .light-br{bottom:22px;right:5px;background:#90EE90;box-shadow:0 0 5px #90EE90;animation:fairyBlink 1.3s ease-in-out infinite 0.9s}
@keyframes fairyBlink{0%,100%{opacity:0.3;transform:scale(0.7)}50%{opacity:1;transform:scale(1.4)}}

/* Photo aspect ratios */
.col-sq{grid-column:span 2;aspect-ratio:1/1}
.col-pt{grid-column:span 2;aspect-ratio:3/4}
.col-ls{grid-column:span 6;aspect-ratio:16/9}

/* Floating hearts decoration */
.float-heart{position:absolute;pointer-events:none;opacity:0;font-size:14px;z-index:2;animation:floatHeart var(--hd,8s) ease-in-out var(--hdel,0s) infinite}
@keyframes floatHeart{0%{opacity:0;transform:translateY(0) scale(0.5) rotate(0deg)}15%{opacity:0.7}70%{opacity:0.4}100%{opacity:0;transform:translateY(-120px) scale(1.1) rotate(25deg)}}

/* Petal rain on collage page */
.petal{position:fixed;pointer-events:none;z-index:15;opacity:0;animation:petalFall var(--pd,7s) ease-in-out var(--pdel,0s) infinite}
@keyframes petalFall{0%{opacity:0;transform:translateY(-20px) translateX(0) rotate(0deg)}10%{opacity:0.55}80%{opacity:0.3}100%{opacity:0;transform:translateY(100vh) translateX(calc(var(--px,30px))) rotate(360deg)}}

/* Photo caption overlay on hover */
.col-item .photo-overlay{position:absolute;bottom:0;left:0;right:0;padding:24px 8px 6px;background:linear-gradient(to top,rgba(0,0,0,0.5) 0%,transparent 100%);opacity:0;transition:opacity 0.4s ease;z-index:4;pointer-events:none}
.col-item.developed:hover .photo-overlay{opacity:1}

/* Title block — full-width centered row between photo sections */
.p3-gap-title{display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;justify-content:center;padding:28px 16px 24px;text-align:center;grid-column:1/-1;position:relative}
.p3-gap-title::before{content:'';position:absolute;inset:0;background:radial-gradient(ellipse at center,rgba(90,20,34,0.4) 0%,transparent 70%);pointer-events:none}
.p3-gap-title .sec-lbl{font-size:11px;letter-spacing:6px;margin-bottom:10px}
.p3-gap-title .main-title{margin-top:2px;font-size:clamp(1.4rem,4.5vw,2.4rem)}
.p3-gap-title .title-line{width:60px;height:1px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,transparent,var(--gold),transparent);margin-top:14px;opacity:0.6}

/* Hanging lights on gallery top */
.gallery-lights{width:100%;max-width:820px;margin:0 auto;position:relative;height:28px;flex-shrink:0;padding:0 8px}
.gl-string{position:absolute;top:4px;left:8px;right:8px;height:1.5px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,transparent 0%,rgba(180,140,80,0.5) 10%,rgba(180,140,80,0.5) 90%,transparent 100%)}
.gl-bulb{position:absolute;top:3px;transform:translateX(-50%);display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center}
.gl-bulb-wire{width:1.5px;height:5px;background:rgba(180,140,80,0.5)}
.gl-bulb-body{width:7px;height:9px;border-radius:50% 50% 40% 40%;animation:bulbFlicker 2s ease-in-out infinite}
.gl-b1{left:8%}.gl-b1 .gl-bulb-body{background:#FFD700;box-shadow:0 0 6px #FFD700;animation-delay:0s}
.gl-b2{left:20%}.gl-b2 .gl-bulb-body{background:#FF69B4;box-shadow:0 0 6px #FF69B4;animation-delay:.3s}
.gl-b3{left:33%}.gl-b3 .gl-bulb-body{background:#87CEEB;box-shadow:0 0 6px #87CEEB;animation-delay:.7s}
.gl-b4{left:46%}.gl-b4 .gl-bulb-body{background:#90EE90;box-shadow:0 0 6px #90EE90;animation-delay:1s}
.gl-b5{left:59%}.gl-b5 .gl-bulb-body{background:#FFB347;box-shadow:0 0 6px #FFB347;animation-delay:.5s}
.gl-b6{left:72%}.gl-b6 .gl-bulb-body{background:#DDA0DD;box-shadow:0 0 6px #DDA0DD;animation-delay:1.2s}
.gl-b7{left:85%}.gl-b7 .gl-bulb-body{background:#FF6B6B;box-shadow:0 0 6px #FF6B6B;animation-delay:.2s}
.gl-b8{left:96%}.gl-b8 .gl-bulb-body{background:#FFD700;box-shadow:0 0 6px #FFD700;animation-delay:.9s}

.p3-footer{flex-shrink:0;padding:6px 16px 80px;text-align:center}

/* LETTER */
.letter-box{background:rgba(255,255,255,0.04);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);border-radius:28px;padding:24px 22px;max-width:560px;width:100%;backdrop-filter:blur(22px);max-height:55vh;overflow-y:auto}
.letter-box::-webkit-scrollbar{width:4px}
.letter-box::-webkit-scrollbar-thumb{background:rgba(232,168,184,.45)}
#letter-text{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:15px;line-height:1.9;color:var(--gold);white-space:pre-line}
#letter-text strong{color:var(--cream)}
#tw-cursor{display:inline-block;width:2px;height:14px;background:var(--pink);vertical-align:text-bottom;animation:blink 1s step-end infinite}
@keyframes blink{0%,100%{opacity:1}50%{opacity:0}}

/* FINAL */
.typewriter-txt{font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:clamp(1.8rem,5vw,3.2rem);font-weight:600;font-style:italic;color:var(--cream);text-align:center;min-height:90px}
.final-msg{font-size:13px;color:var(--gold);text-align:center;margin-top:18px}
.rate-box{margin-top:28px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:10px}
.rate-stars{display:flex;gap:8px;flex-wrap:wrap;justify-content:center}
.star-r{font-size:24px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.2);cursor:pointer;transition:transform 0.18s ease}
.star-r:hover,.star-r.hover{transform:scale(1.2);color:rgba(232,168,184,.7)}
.star-r.active{color:var(--pink);text-shadow:0 0 12px rgba(232,168,184,.8)}

#spotify{position:fixed;bottom:15px;right:15px;z-index:200;background:rgba(10,5,12,.9);border:1px solid rgba(232,168,184,.2);border-radius:18px;padding:8px 12px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;backdrop-filter:blur(20px);min-width:180px}
.sp-art{width:35px;height:35px;border-radius:8px;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#6b1835,#220810);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;position:relative}
.sp-disc{position:absolute;width:14px;height:14px;border-radius:50%;border:2px solid rgba(255,190,170,.3);animation:spin 5s linear infinite}
@keyframes spin{to{transform:rotate(360deg)}}
.sp-info{flex:1}
.sp-track-name{font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-size:11px;color:rgba(245,230,211,.9)}
.sp-eq{display:flex;align-items:flex-end;gap:2px;height:16px}
.sp-eq span{width:2px;background:rgba(210,95,120,.7);animation:eq 1s ease-in-out infinite}
.sp-eq span:nth-child(1){height:4px;animation-delay:0s}.sp-eq span:nth-child(2){height:10px;animation-delay:.12s}.sp-eq span:nth-child(3){height:6px;animation-delay:.24s}.sp-eq span:nth-child(4){height:12px;animation-delay:.18s}.sp-eq span:nth-child(5){height:4px;animation-delay:.06s}
@keyframes eq{0%,100%{transform:scaleY(0.3)}50%{transform:scaleY(1)}}

canvas#cfcan{position:fixed;inset:0;z-index:800;pointer-events:none;display:none}
.cp{position:fixed;pointer-events:none;z-index:10000;border-radius:50%;animation:cpf 0.7s ease-out forwards}
@keyframes cpf{0%{opacity:0.8;transform:scale(1)}100%{opacity:0;transform:scale(0) translateY(-18px)}}
.reveal{opacity:0;animation:revealUp .6s forwards}
@keyframes revealUp{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)}to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0)}}
@media(max-width:480px){
  .cd-box{padding:10px 12px;min-width:55px}
  .cd-num{font-size:1.5rem}
  .col-sq,.col-pt{grid-column:span 3}
  .col-ls{grid-column:span 6}
  .collage-grid{gap:6px;padding:6px 8px 12px}
  .p3-gap-title{padding:20px 12px 16px}
}

/* Vignette overlay on collage page */
.collage-vignette{position:absolute;inset:0;pointer-events:none;z-index:6;background:radial-gradient(ellipse at center,transparent 60%,rgba(14,3,6,0.5) 100%)}

/* Ribbon decoration */
.ribbon-deco{position:absolute;width:100%;height:2px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,transparent 0%,rgba(232,168,184,0.3) 20%,rgba(232,200,168,0.5) 50%,rgba(232,168,184,0.3) 80%,transparent 100%);z-index:5;pointer-events:none}
.ribbon-deco::before,.ribbon-deco::after{content:'✦';position:absolute;top:-6px;font-size:10px;color:var(--gold);opacity:0.5}
.ribbon-deco::before{left:20%}
.ribbon-deco::after{right:20%}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div id="stars"></div>
<div id="sparkles-container"></div>
<canvas id="cfcan"></canvas>
<div id="overlay"></div>

<!-- PAGE 1: COUNTDOWN -->
<div class="page active" id="page1">
  <div class="sec-lbl reveal">Counting Down</div>
  <div class="main-title reveal">Your Special Day<br><span style="font-size:.55em;font-weight:400;display:block;margin-top:5px">16 June 2026</span></div>
  <p class="subtitle reveal" style="font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-style:italic">Something beautiful is waiting for you</p>
  <div class="cd-row reveal" id="cdRow">
    <div class="cd-box"><span class="cd-num" id="cdD">00</span><span class="cd-lbl">Days</span></div>
    <div class="cd-sep">:</div>
    <div class="cd-box"><span class="cd-num" id="cdH">00</span><span class="cd-lbl">Hours</span></div>
    <div class="cd-sep">:</div>
    <div class="cd-box"><span class="cd-num" id="cdM">00</span><span class="cd-lbl">Minutes</span></div>
    <div class="cd-sep">:</div>
    <div class="cd-box" id="secondsBox"><span class="cd-num" id="cdS">00</span><span class="cd-lbl">Seconds</span></div>
  </div>
  <button class="btn btn-pink reveal" id="nextBtn" onclick="toPage(2)" style="display:none">✦ &nbsp;Open Your Gift&nbsp; ✦</button>
</div>

<!-- PAGE 2: CAKE — header stays on top, cake stays below -->
<div class="page" id="page2">
  <div class="p2-header">
    <div class="sec-lbl" style="justify-content:center">A Small Surprise For You</div>
    <div class="main-title" style="font-size:clamp(1.2rem,3.5vw,2rem)">Happy Birthday, Yokhe</div>
  </div>
  <div class="page2-content">
    <!-- Hanging string lights above cake -->
    <div class="cake-lights">
      <div class="lights-string"></div>
      <div class="light-bulb lb1"></div>
      <div class="light-bulb lb2"></div>
      <div class="light-bulb lb3"></div>
      <div class="light-bulb lb4"></div>
      <div class="light-bulb lb5"></div>
      <div class="light-bulb lb6"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="cake-container" onclick="openGift()">
      <div class="cake-layer-top">
        <div class="cake-icing">
          <div class="icing-dot"></div><div class="icing-dot"></div><div class="icing-dot"></div><div class="icing-dot"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="candle"><div class="flame"></div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="cake-layer"></div>
      <div class="cake-layer"></div>
      <div class="cake-plate"></div>
    </div>
    <p class="gift-hint">Tap the cake to open your gift</p>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- PAGE 3: PUZZLE COLLAGE GALLERY -->
<div class="page" id="page3">
  <div id="petal-container"></div>
  <div class="p3-inner">
    <!-- Hanging gallery lights -->
    <div class="gallery-lights">
      <div class="gl-string"></div>
      <div class="gl-bulb gl-b1"><div class="gl-bulb-wire"></div><div class="gl-bulb-body"></div></div>
      <div class="gl-bulb gl-b2"><div class="gl-bulb-wire"></div><div class="gl-bulb-body"></div></div>
      <div class="gl-bulb gl-b3"><div class="gl-bulb-wire"></div><div class="gl-bulb-body"></div></div>
      <div class="gl-bulb gl-b4"><div class="gl-bulb-wire"></div><div class="gl-bulb-body"></div></div>
      <div class="gl-bulb gl-b5"><div class="gl-bulb-wire"></div><div class="gl-bulb-body"></div></div>
      <div class="gl-bulb gl-b6"><div class="gl-bulb-wire"></div><div class="gl-bulb-body"></div></div>
      <div class="gl-bulb gl-b7"><div class="gl-bulb-wire"></div><div class="gl-bulb-body"></div></div>
      <div class="gl-bulb gl-b8"><div class="gl-bulb-wire"></div><div class="gl-bulb-body"></div></div>
    </div>
    <div class="collage-scroll" id="collageScroll">
      <div class="collage-grid" id="pol-grid3">
        <!-- Row 1: sq + sq + portrait -->
        <div class="col-item col-sq" style="grid-column:1/3"><div class="pol-frame"></div><div class="shimmer"></div><div class="photo-overlay"></div><div class="light-tl"></div><div class="light-tr"></div><div class="light-bl"></div><div class="light-br"></div><img src="https://i.ibb.co.com/PyRKBQX/IMG-20251005-111037.jpg" loading="lazy"></div>
        <div class="col-item col-sq" style="grid-column:3/5"><div class="pol-frame"></div><div class="shimmer"></div><div class="photo-overlay"></div><div class="light-tl"></div><div class="light-tr"></div><div class="light-bl"></div><div class="light-br"></div><img src="https://i.ibb.co.com/spF49p3q/IMG-20251019-WA0047.jpg" loading="lazy"></div>
        <div class="col-item col-sq" style="grid-column:5/7"><div class="pol-frame"></div><div class="shimmer"></div><div class="photo-overlay"></div><div class="light-tl"></div><div class="light-tr"></div><div class="light-bl"></div><div class="light-br"></div><img src="https://i.ibb.co.com/WW86JfTp/IMG-20250831-WA0004.jpg" loading="lazy"></div>
        <!-- Ribbon decoration -->
        <div class="ribbon-deco" style="grid-column:1/-1"></div>
        <!-- Title - centered full-width row -->
        <div class="p3-gap-title" style="grid-column:1/-1">
          <div class="sec-lbl" style="justify-content:center">✦ Just Yokhe ✦</div>
          <div class="main-title">It's Your Special Day</div>
          <div class="title-line"></div>
        </div>
        <!-- Ribbon decoration -->
        <div class="ribbon-deco" style="grid-column:1/-1"></div>
        <!-- Row 2 portrait trio -->
        <div class="col-item col-pt" style="grid-column:1/3"><div class="pol-frame"></div><div class="shimmer"></div><div class="photo-overlay"></div><div class="light-tl"></div><div class="light-tr"></div><div class="light-bl"></div><div class="light-br"></div><img src="https://i.ibb.co.com/3y6nVRWM/IMG-20251005-WA0010.jpg" loading="lazy"></div>
        <div class="col-item col-pt" style="grid-column:3/5"><div class="pol-frame"></div><div class="shimmer"></div><div class="photo-overlay"></div><div class="light-tl"></div><div class="light-tr"></div><div class="light-bl"></div><div class="light-br"></div><img src="https://i.ibb.co.com/dsn3Pc3X/IMG-20251005-WA0012.jpg" loading="lazy"></div>
        <div class="col-item col-pt" style="grid-column:5/7"><div class="pol-frame"></div><div class="shimmer"></div><div class="photo-overlay"></div><div class="light-tl"></div><div class="light-tr"></div><div class="light-bl"></div><div class="light-br"></div><img src="https://i.ibb.co.com/tjYms8b/IMG-20251005-WA0014.jpg" loading="lazy"></div>
        <!-- Landscape 1 -->
        <div class="col-item col-ls"><div class="pol-frame"></div><div class="shimmer"></div><div class="photo-overlay"></div><div class="light-tl"></div><div class="light-tr"></div><div class="light-bl"></div><div class="light-br"></div><img src="https://i.ibb.co.com/KjVYnQfX/IMG-20251005-WA0015.jpg" loading="lazy"></div>
        <!-- Row 3 portrait trio -->
        <div class="col-item col-pt" style="grid-column:1/3"><div class="pol-frame"></div><div class="shimmer"></div><div class="photo-overlay"></div><div class="light-tl"></div><div class="light-tr"></div><div class="light-bl"></div><div class="light-br"></div><img src="https://i.ibb.co.com/5xcTRF5F/IMG-20251005-WA0019.jpg" loading="lazy"></div>
        <div class="col-item col-pt" style="grid-column:3/5"><div class="pol-frame"></div><div class="shimmer"></div><div class="photo-overlay"></div><div class="light-tl"></div><div class="light-tr"></div><div class="light-bl"></div><div class="light-br"></div><img src="https://i.ibb.co.com/z0FN3Lk/IMG-20251005-WA0021.jpg" loading="lazy"></div>
        <div class="col-item col-pt" style="grid-column:5/7"><div class="pol-frame"></div><div class="shimmer"></div><div class="photo-overlay"></div><div class="light-tl"></div><div class="light-tr"></div><div class="light-bl"></div><div class="light-br"></div><img src="https://i.ibb.co.com/bR86VZT9/Whats-App-Image-2026-06-15-at-15-14-15.jpg" loading="lazy"></div>
        <!-- Landscape 2 -->
        <div class="col-item col-ls"><div class="pol-frame"></div><div class="shimmer"></div><div class="photo-overlay"></div><div class="light-tl"></div><div class="light-tr"></div><div class="light-bl"></div><div class="light-br"></div><img src="https://i.ibb.co.com/cSrs5pTk/IMG-20251005-WA0017.jpg" loading="lazy"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="p3-footer">
      <button class="btn btn-pink" onclick="toPage(4)" id="btn-p3" style="display:none">✦ &nbsp;Read My Letter &nbsp;→</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- PAGE 4: LETTER -->
<div class="page" id="page4">
  <h1 class="main-title" style="margin-bottom:15px;font-size:clamp(1.5rem,4vw,2.3rem)">Happy Birthday, Yokhe</h1>
  <div class="letter-box" id="letterBox">
    <div class="lt-title">A Letter from me</div>
    <div id="letter-text"></div>
    <div class="lt-sig" id="lt-sig" style="display:none">With all my best wishes, always</div>
  </div>
  <button class="btn" onclick="toPage(8)" style="margin-top:18px;display:none" id="btn-letter">Continue →</button>
</div>

<!-- FINAL PAGE -->
<div class="page final-page" id="page8">
  <div class="typewriter-txt" id="tw-txt"></div>
  <p class="final-msg">Thank you for being such a wonderful friend.<br>Wishing you all the best on your special day.</p>
  <div class="rate-box">
    <p class="rate-lbl">Rate this birthday gift</p>
    <div class="rate-stars" id="rate-stars">
      <span class="star-r" data-v="1">★</span><span class="star-r" data-v="2">★</span><span class="star-r" data-v="3">★</span><span class="star-r" data-v="4">★</span><span class="star-r" data-v="5">★</span>
      <span class="star-r" data-v="6">★</span><span class="star-r" data-v="7">★</span><span class="star-r" data-v="8">★</span><span class="star-r" data-v="9">★</span><span class="star-r" data-v="10">★</span>
    </div>
    <p id="rate-hint" style="font-size:11px;color:var(--gold);min-height:18px"></p>
  </div>
  <button class="btn" onclick="doReplay()" style="margin-top:20px">↺ Replay</button>
</div>

<div id="spotify"><div class="sp-art"><div class="sp-disc"></div><span class="sp-note">♪</span></div><div class="sp-info"><div class="sp-now-lbl">Now Playing</div><div class="sp-track-name">Happy Birthday To You</div><div class="sp-artist-name">Piano & Strings</div></div><div class="sp-eq"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></div></div>

<script>
// Stars
const starsEl=document.getElementById('stars');
for(let i=0;i<110;i++){const s=document.createElement('div');s.className='star';s.style.left=Math.random()*100+'%';s.style.top=Math.random()*100+'%';let sz=Math.random()*2.5+0.6;s.style.width=sz+'px';s.style.height=sz+'px';s.style.setProperty('--dur',(Math.random()*3+2)+'s');s.style.setProperty('--del',Math.random()*4+'s');starsEl.appendChild(s);}

// Sparkles
const sparklesEl=document.getElementById('sparkles-container');
function spawnSparkle(){const h=document.createElement('div');h.className='fsparkle';h.textContent=['✨','🌸','✦','🌟','✧'][Math.floor(Math.random()*5)];h.style.left=Math.random()*100+'%';h.style.bottom='-20px';h.style.setProperty('--fdur',(Math.random()*6+8)+'s');sparklesEl.appendChild(h);setTimeout(()=>h.remove(),13000);}
setInterval(spawnSparkle,2000);

// Audio
let musicOn=false,audioCtx=null;
function initAudio(){if(musicOn)return;musicOn=true;try{audioCtx=new(window.AudioContext||window.webkitAudioContext)();if(audioCtx.state==='suspended')audioCtx.resume();setTimeout(playHBD,5000);}catch(e){}}
function playNote(freq,startSec,durSec,vol=0.13){if(!audioCtx||!freq)return;const now=audioCtx.currentTime;[{type:'sine',vol:vol*0.7},{type:'triangle',vol:vol*0.3}].forEach(({type,vol:v})=>{const osc=audioCtx.createOscillator(),gain=audioCtx.createGain();osc.connect(gain);gain.connect(audioCtx.destination);osc.type=type;osc.frequency.value=freq;gain.gain.setValueAtTime(0,now+startSec);gain.gain.linearRampToValueAtTime(v,now+startSec+0.01);gain.gain.exponentialRampToValueAtTime(v*0.55,now+startSec+0.07);gain.gain.linearRampToValueAtTime(0.0001,now+startSec+durSec);osc.start(now+startSec);osc.stop(now+startSec+durSec+0.04);});}
function playHBD(){const F4=349.23,G4=392,A4=440,Bb4=466.16,C5=523.25,D5=587.33,E5=659.25,F5=698.46;const bpm=78,b=60/bpm;const song=[[F4,0.0,0.4],[F4,0.45,0.2],[G4,0.7,0.9],[F4,1.7,0.9],[Bb4,2.7,0.9],[A4,3.7,1.7],[F4,5.8,0.4],[F4,6.25,0.2],[G4,6.5,0.9],[F4,7.5,0.9],[C5,8.5,0.9],[Bb4,9.5,1.7],[F4,11.6,0.4],[F4,12.05,0.2],[F5,12.3,0.9],[D5,13.3,0.9],[Bb4,14.3,0.55],[A4,14.9,0.55],[G4,15.5,1.5],[E5,17.2,0.4],[E5,17.65,0.2],[D5,17.9,0.9],[Bb4,18.9,0.9],[C5,19.9,0.9],[Bb4,20.9,1.8]];const totalBeats=23;song.forEach(([f,s,d])=>playNote(f,s*b,d*b));setTimeout(()=>{if(musicOn)playHBD();},totalBeats*b*1000);}
document.addEventListener('click',initAudio,{once:true});
document.addEventListener('touchstart',initAudio,{once:true});

// COUNTDOWN
let targetReached=false, alarmInterval=null, timerFinished=false;
let targetTime=new Date(2026,5,16,0,0,0,0); // 16 June 2026
const nextBtn=document.getElementById('nextBtn');
const secondsBox=document.getElementById('secondsBox');
const cdRow=document.getElementById('cdRow');
const cdS=document.getElementById('cdS');

function vibrate(pattern){
  if(navigator.vibrate){
    try{navigator.vibrate(pattern);}catch(e){}
  }
}

function showAlarmMode(){
  if(targetReached) return;
  targetReached=true;
  let startTime=Date.now();
  const ALARM_DURATION=3000;
  // Show millisecond countdown in the seconds box — no shaking, no vibration yet
  secondsBox.classList.add('millisecond-box');
  alarmInterval=setInterval(()=>{
    if(timerFinished) return;
    const elapsed=Date.now()-startTime;
    const remaining=Math.max(0,ALARM_DURATION-elapsed);
    if(remaining<=0){
      clearInterval(alarmInterval);
      secondsBox.classList.remove('millisecond-box');
      cdS.textContent='00';
      timerFinished=true;
      nextBtn.style.display='inline-flex';
      nextBtn.classList.add('highlight-btn');
      nextBtn.classList.remove('btn-disabled');
      // True 0:00:00:00 reached — boxes turn red with a brief pulse + buzz
      cdRow.classList.add('cd-zero');
      vibrate([200,80,200,80,400]);
      return;
    }
    const sec=Math.floor(remaining/1000);
    const ms=remaining%1000;
    cdS.textContent=sec+':'+String(ms).padStart(3,'0');
  },16);
}

function updateCountdown(){
  if(targetReached) return;
  let now=new Date();
  let diff=targetTime-now;
  if(diff<=0&&!targetReached){showAlarmMode();setCD('cdD',0);setCD('cdH',0);setCD('cdM',0);setCD('cdS',0);return;}
  if(diff<0)diff=0;
  setCD('cdD',Math.floor(diff/86400000));
  setCD('cdH',Math.floor((diff%86400000)/3600000));
  setCD('cdM',Math.floor((diff%3600000)/60000));
  setCD('cdS',Math.floor((diff%60000)/1000),true);
}
function setCD(id,value,animate=false){const el=document.getElementById(id);if(!el)return;const str=String(value).padStart(2,'0');if(el.textContent!==str){el.textContent=str;if(animate&&!targetReached){el.classList.remove('pop');void el.offsetWidth;el.classList.add('pop');}}}
nextBtn.classList.add('btn-disabled');
setInterval(updateCountdown,200);
updateCountdown();

let curPage=1, p3Revealed=false;
function revealP3Grid(){
  if(p3Revealed) return;
  p3Revealed=true;
  const pols=document.querySelectorAll('#pol-grid3 .col-item');
  pols.forEach((p,i)=>{
    setTimeout(()=>{
      p.classList.add('reveal-pol');
      setTimeout(()=>{p.classList.add('developed');},500);
    },i*90);
  });
  const totalDelay=pols.length*90+700;
  setTimeout(()=>{document.getElementById('btn-p3').style.display='inline-flex';},totalDelay);
  // Hybrid auto-scroll: very slow, gentle scroll that stops permanently
  // the moment the user interacts.
  setTimeout(()=>{
    const scroll=document.getElementById('collageScroll');
    if(!scroll)return;
    const totalH=scroll.scrollHeight-scroll.clientHeight;
    if(totalH<=0)return;
    let cancelled=false;
    let start=null;
    const isMobile='ontouchstart' in window||navigator.maxTouchPoints>0;
    if(isMobile)return; // Disable auto-scroll on mobile — causes jitter
    const dur=40000; // 40s — very slow, relaxing scroll
    function cancelAutoScroll(){
      if(cancelled)return;
      cancelled=true;
      ['wheel','touchstart','pointerdown','scroll','keydown'].forEach(e=>scroll.removeEventListener(e,onUserScroll));
    }
    function onUserScroll(){
      cancelAutoScroll();
    }
    ['wheel','touchstart','pointerdown','keydown'].forEach(e=>scroll.addEventListener(e,onUserScroll,{passive:true}));
    // Also cancel if user scrolls via any means (scroll event with debounce)
    let lastAutoTop=-1;
    scroll.addEventListener('scroll',function(){
      if(cancelled)return;
      if(lastAutoTop>=0&&Math.abs(scroll.scrollTop-lastAutoTop)>3){
        cancelAutoScroll();
      }
    },{passive:true});
    function autoScroll(ts){
      if(cancelled)return;
      if(!start)start=ts;
      const prog=Math.min((ts-start)/dur,1);
      // Smooth ease-in-out
      const ease=prog<0.5?2*prog*prog:1-Math.pow(-2*prog+2,2)/2;
      lastAutoTop=ease*totalH;
      scroll.scrollTop=lastAutoTop;
      if(prog<1)requestAnimationFrame(autoScroll);
      else cancelAutoScroll();
    }
    requestAnimationFrame(autoScroll);
  },totalDelay+600);
}

function toPage(n){
  if(n===2&&!timerFinished)return;
  initAudio();
  const ov=document.getElementById('overlay');
  ov.style.opacity='1';
  ov.style.pointerEvents='all';
  setTimeout(()=>{
    document.getElementById('page'+curPage).classList.remove('active');
    curPage=n;
    document.getElementById('page'+n).classList.add('active');
    if(n===3)revealP3Grid();
    if(n===4)startLetter();
    if(n===8)startFinalTW();
    ov.style.opacity='0';
    ov.style.pointerEvents='none';
  },470);
}

// FIX REPLAY BUG: fully reset all state
function doReplay(){
  targetReached=false;
  alarmInterval=null;
  timerFinished=false;
  musicOn=false;
  if(audioCtx){try{audioCtx.close();}catch(e){}audioCtx=null;}
  giftOpened=false;
  p3Revealed=false;
  letterInterval=null;
  // Reset pages
  document.querySelectorAll('.page').forEach(p=>p.classList.remove('active'));
  document.getElementById('page1').classList.add('active');
  curPage=1;
  // Reset countdown button
  nextBtn.style.display='none';
  nextBtn.classList.add('btn-disabled');
  nextBtn.classList.remove('highlight-btn');
  // Reset gallery
  document.querySelectorAll('#pol-grid3 .col-item').forEach(p=>{p.classList.remove('reveal-pol','developed');});
  document.getElementById('btn-p3').style.display='none';
  // Reset letter
  document.getElementById('letter-text').innerHTML='';
  document.getElementById('lt-sig').style.display='none';
  document.getElementById('btn-letter').style.display='none';
  // Restart countdown
  cdRow.classList.remove('cd-zero');
  secondsBox.classList.remove('millisecond-box');
  setInterval(updateCountdown,200);
  updateCountdown();
}

let giftOpened=false;
function openGift(){
  if(giftOpened||!timerFinished)return;
  giftOpened=true;
  initAudio();
  const cc=document.getElementById('cfcan');
  cc.width=innerWidth;cc.height=innerHeight;cc.style.display='block';
  const cx=cc.getContext('2d');
  let pieces=[],frame=0,lastTime=performance.now();
  const colors=['#e8a8b8','#e8c8a8','#f5e6d3','#fff9f0','#c87090','#ffd4e8'];
  for(let i=0;i<160;i++){let angle=Math.random()*Math.PI*2,speed=100+Math.random()*150;pieces.push({x:innerWidth/2,y:innerHeight/2-60,vx:Math.cos(angle)*speed,vy:Math.sin(angle)*speed-50,w:5+Math.random()*8,h:6+Math.random()*10,rot:Math.random()*Math.PI*2,vrot:(Math.random()-0.5)*0.2,color:colors[Math.floor(Math.random()*colors.length)],opacity:1,gravity:170});}
  function animateConfetti(now){const dt=Math.min((now-lastTime)/1000,0.05);lastTime=now;cx.clearRect(0,0,cc.width,cc.height);pieces.forEach(p=>{p.vy+=p.gravity*dt;p.x+=p.vx*dt;p.y+=p.vy*dt;p.rot+=p.vrot;if(frame>50)p.opacity-=0.012;cx.save();cx.globalAlpha=Math.max(0,p.opacity);cx.translate(p.x,p.y);cx.rotate(p.rot);cx.fillStyle=p.color;cx.fillRect(-p.w/2,-p.h/2,p.w,p.h);cx.restore();});frame++;if(frame<200)requestAnimationFrame(animateConfetti);else{cc.style.display='none';setTimeout(()=>toPage(3),300);}}
  requestAnimationFrame(animateConfetti);
}

const LETTER_RAW=`Happy birthday **Yokhebed Yoan Yemima Da Costa**!

Wish you all the best panjang umur, sehat selalu, and may your life be filled with beautiful things you truly deserve.

Semoga apa yang kamu impikan bisa tercapai, and may every step forward bring you closer to everything you've always dreamed of.

Good luck for your next journey in Jakarta! Semoga sukses terus di sana. The city is lucky to have you. Surabaya is gonna be so quiet after you leave :(( but I'm so excited to hear your stories there

Thank you for being my friend, genuinely grateful to have you around. You make everything brighter just by being you.

God bless you always, Yokhe! `;

function renderBold(text){return text.replace(/\*\*(.*?)\*\*/g,'<strong>$1</strong>');}
let letterInterval=null,letterBoxElement=null;
function startLetter(){const el=document.getElementById('letter-text');el.innerHTML='';let idx=0;const plain=LETTER_RAW.replace(/\*\*(.*?)\*\*/g,'$1');let shown='';if(letterInterval)clearInterval(letterInterval);letterBoxElement=document.getElementById('letterBox');letterInterval=setInterval(()=>{if(idx>=plain.length){clearInterval(letterInterval);el.innerHTML=renderBold(LETTER_RAW).replace(/\n/g,'<br>');document.getElementById('lt-sig').style.display='block';document.getElementById('btn-letter').style.display='inline-flex';if(letterBoxElement)letterBoxElement.scrollTop=letterBoxElement.scrollHeight;return;}let ch=plain[idx];if(ch==='\n'){shown+='<br>';if(plain[idx+1]==='\n'){shown+='<br>';idx++;}}else{shown+=(ch==="'"?'&#39;':ch);}el.innerHTML=shown+'<span id="tw-cursor"></span>';idx++;if(letterBoxElement)letterBoxElement.scrollTop=letterBoxElement.scrollHeight;},22);}

const FINAL_TEXTS=['Happy Birthday','from the bottom of my heart','God BlG3r4ld4rthur#gess You Always','Stay Amazing'];
function startFinalTW(){const el=document.getElementById('tw-txt');let ti=0,ci=0,del=false;function type(){const ct=FINAL_TEXTS[ti];if(del){el.textContent=ct.substring(0,ci-1);ci--;}else{el.textContent=ct.substring(0,ci+1);ci++;}let spd=del?45:90;if(!del&&ci===ct.length){spd=1800;del=true;}else if(del&&ci===0){del=false;ti=(ti+1)%FINAL_TEXTS.length;spd=450;}setTimeout(type,spd);}type();}

if(window.matchMedia('(hover:hover)').matches){let lastP=0;document.addEventListener('mousemove',e=>{const now=Date.now();if(now-lastP<55)return;lastP=now;for(let i=0;i<2;i++){const p=document.createElement('div');p.className='cp';const sz=2+Math.random()*5;const cols=['rgba(232,168,184,.85)','rgba(232,200,168,.7)','rgba(200,120,160,.8)'];p.style.cssText=`left:${e.clientX+(Math.random()-.5)*14}px;top:${e.clientY+(Math.random()-.5)*14}px;width:${sz}px;height:${sz}px;background:${cols[Math.floor(Math.random()*cols.length)]}`;document.body.appendChild(p);setTimeout(()=>p.remove(),1000);}});}

// Petal rain on collage page
function spawnPetals(){
  const container=document.getElementById('petal-container');
  if(!container)return;
  const petals=['🌸','🩷','✿','❀','💗'];
  function addPetal(){
    if(curPage!==3)return;
    const p=document.createElement('div');
    p.className='petal';
    p.textContent=petals[Math.floor(Math.random()*petals.length)];
    p.style.left=Math.random()*100+'%';
    p.style.fontSize=(10+Math.random()*10)+'px';
    p.style.setProperty('--pd',(6+Math.random()*6)+'s');
    p.style.setProperty('--pdel','0s');
    p.style.setProperty('--px',(Math.random()*60-30)+'px');
    container.appendChild(p);
    setTimeout(()=>p.remove(),14000);
  }
  setInterval(addPetal,1800);
}
spawnPetals();

(function(){const stars=document.querySelectorAll('#rate-stars .star-r');const hint=document.getElementById('rate-hint');let locked=false;stars.forEach(star=>{star.addEventListener('mouseenter',()=>{if(locked)return;const v=parseInt(star.dataset.v);stars.forEach(s=>s.classList.toggle('hover',parseInt(s.dataset.v)<=v));});star.addEventListener('mouseleave',()=>{if(locked)return;stars.forEach(s=>s.classList.remove('hover'));});star.addEventListener('click',()=>{if(locked)return;locked=true;const v=parseInt(star.dataset.v);stars.forEach(s=>s.classList.toggle('active',parseInt(s.dataset.v)<=v));if(hint)hint.textContent=`Thanks for ${v}/10! Opening WhatsApp...`;const msg=encodeURIComponent(`✨ Birthday Gift Rating ✨\n\nRating: ${v}/10\nFrom: Yokhebed Yoan Yemima Da Costa\n\nGenerated by arthurg.my.id/yokhe`);setTimeout(()=>{window.location.href='https://wa.me/6285102775181?text='+msg;},800);});star.addEventListener('touchend',(e)=>{e.preventDefault();star.click();});});})();
</script>
</body>
</html>

<!--
=======================================================================
📋 PANDUAN DEPLOY KE arthurg.my.id/yokhe (VPS Ubuntu + SSL aktif)
=======================================================================

LANGKAH 1 — Upload file
  Dari PC/laptop kamu, copy file ini ke VPS via SCP:
    scp yokhee.html user@ALAMAT_IP_VPS:/var/www/html/yokhe.html

  Atau kalau pakai FileZilla / SFTP, upload ke folder:
    /var/www/html/yokhe.html
  (sesuaikan path jika website utama kamu ada di folder lain,
   misal /var/www/arthurg.my.id/public_html/)

LANGKAH 2 — Cek config Nginx kamu
  Edit file config Nginx website kamu:
    sudo nano /etc/nginx/sites-available/arthurg.my.id

  Pastikan di dalam blok server ada baris seperti ini:
    root /var/www/html;         ← sesuaikan dengan folder aktual kamu

  Dengan root yang benar, file yokhe.html otomatis bisa diakses via:
    https://arthurg.my.id/yokhe.html
  ATAU kalau mau tanpa ekstensi .html, tambahkan di blok location:

    location /yokhe {
        alias /var/www/html/yokhe.html;
        default_type text/html;
    }

  Simpan file (Ctrl+O, Enter, Ctrl+X).

LANGKAH 3 — Reload Nginx
    sudo nginx -t              ← test config dulu, pastikan "OK"
    sudo systemctl reload nginx

LANGKAH 4 — Akses
  Buka browser → https://arthurg.my.id/yokhe
  (atau /yokhe.html jika tidak pakai alias)

TIPS:
  - File ini 100% self-contained HTML, tidak perlu node/npm/build step.
  - SSL sudah aktif di domain kamu, jadi tidak perlu setup Certbot lagi.
  - Kalau mau update isi foto/teks, tinggal edit file HTML-nya
    dan upload ulang via scp atau SFTP.
  - Untuk cek error Nginx: sudo journalctl -u nginx --no-pager -n 30

=======================================================================
-->
